title: GR10 Matching Pool Breakdown
body:
This Snapshot vote is proposed by 🔥_🔥, looking to finalize a decision around the Gitcoin Grants Round 10 allocations proposed and discussed in this [forum post](https://gov.gitcoin.co/t/proposal-gitcoin-round-10-matching-pool-allocations/4988).

There have been no new proposals to support option 3, but we have included it for the sake of neutrality. 


The three options to vote on are described below:

### Option 1:

Distribute the matching pool pro-rata relative to the quadratic formula using one bucket and no specified categories.

### Option 2:
Distribute the matching pool based on the following breakdown. These allocations have been proposed by the Gitcoin Core team alongside 🔥_🔥

- Infrastructure: 30%
- Dapp Tech: 25%
- Community: 20%
- Latin America 10%
- NFTs: 7.5%
- dGov: 7.5%

### Option 3:

A new proposal should be submitted with different allocations. 


**This proposal and vote looks to finalize the allocation of Grants Round 10 matching funds before the beginning of the round.**
